snippet.textDisplay: NO doubt in my mind it was Tariq. As much as Tasha may have wanted to kill Ghost, I didn't see any motivation in the episodes leading up to a reason she would actually want to go through with it. It may be a sleight of hand Power is playing, but everything is pointing to Tariq doing it, and Tasha possibly 'covering' for him after the fact. I don't 'believe' Ghost would have said "Let it go" had it been Tasha, nor would he have really been shocked all that much she did it... now, if Tariq came back and killed him, it would been the ultimate betrayal, and something Ghost would have never saw coming.
